*Mislio sam da æu uspeti u tome.(I thought I would succeed in it.) 
*Æu sve uraditi da bih bio uspešan.(I will do everything to be successful.)
*Nadam se da æu imati priliku da odem tamo.(I hope I will have a chance to go there.) 
*Nastaviæu da se trudim da postignem uspeh.(I will keep trying to achieve success.) 
*Želim da æu imati priliku da odem do tamo.(I want to have a chance to go there.)